article_id:2911,category_name:Events,title_name:A Raid Event Revival, Dawn of Dragalia, Is Coming Soon!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/de39770f6b52a3fb24199ed89fc6941f.png,message:<div>The Dawn of Dragalia raid event returns on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1664517600"></span>! During this event, you can use co-op play to fight against a raid boss with no elemental attunement.</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/de39770f6b52a3fb24199ed89fc6941f.png"></div><div>This event&#39;s theme song is &quot;Because of You&quot; and was sung by Setsuko, written and composed by Taku Inoue, and arranged by Teruaki &quot;EDDY&quot; Tanahashi.<br><br>■Event Duration<br><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1664517600"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1665381599"></span><br><br>■Notes<br>1. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign to participate in event quests.<br>2. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign to play co-op.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1664258400,update_time1646190783